author: Times Report
title: CHS fall athletes bundle up to support Boys' Soccer
text: CHS fall athletes bundle up to support Boys' Soccer Crookston High School fall athletes bundled up and filled the bleachers to support the Pirate Boys’ Soccer team during the Section Playoff game Thursday against East Grand Forks. Comment Posted Oct. 16, 2015 at 11:56 AM By Times Report Posted Oct. 16, 2015 at 11:56 AM Crookston, Minn. Crookston High School fall athletes bundled up and filled the bleachers to support the Pirate Boys’ Soccer team during the Section Playoff game Thursday against East Grand Forks.
